      "rationale": "FDA GCBP experimental data covers flow rates 2–8 L/min and rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM. COU operating envelope spans 2.5–6 L/min and 2200–3200 RPM, giving 100% coverage of the COU envelope. Test fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C, Hct 33%) are representative of CPB conditions."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
