      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within ±15% at all five validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values agreed with experimental measurements within 9% at all five operating points (max deviation 8.7% at 4 L/min, 2800 RPM). The acceptance criterion of ±15% is satisfied at all operating points, providing confidence in the model's predictive capability for the COU."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
