      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump, which is geometrically representative of the Class II CPB device under assessment. Operating conditions overlap fully with the COU envelope. The validation hierarchy is appropriate for MRL 2, with component-level and system-level validation activities both completed."
    },
    {
