      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form uncertainty is acknowledged but not formally quantified.",
      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model and power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) are standard choices for CFD hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged as a limitation but formal quantification is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
