      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal input values with documented sources are sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients were sourced from published literature and FDA benchmark documentation. Sensitivity to input uncertainty is not formally quantified at MRL 2 but nominal values are well-established for bovine blood at CPB conditions."
